---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="GOLDEN FITNESS GYM · Gimnasio en El Cerrito, Kanasín"
  description="El estándar dorado para entrenar en Kanasín. ⭐ 4.5 con 84 reseñas en Google. Buenos entrenadores, instalaciones de primera. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen"
  ogImage="/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen/img/foto_1.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@500;600;700&family=Mulish:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
  favicon="🏅"
  themeColor="#0d0d0d"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529994412918"}
  telefono={"999 441 2918"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=11600852925967987399&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="gf">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="wrap hero-in">
        <p class="kicker reveal">Gimnasio · El Cerrito, Kanasín</p>
        <h1 class="word reveal">
          <span class="word-gold">GOLDEN</span>
          <span class="word-cream">FITNESS GYM</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="tagline reveal">El estándar dorado para entrenar en Kanasín: buenos entrenadores, instalaciones de primera y el ambiente que te hace volver todos los días.</p>

        <div class="badge-row reveal">
          <span class="sprig sprig--sm" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
          <span class="badge-txt">Estándar dorado del entrenamiento</span>
          <span class="sprig sprig--sm sprig--r" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
        </div>

        <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=11600852925967987399&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.5 · 84 reseñas en Google
        </a>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/529994412918" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18.2c-1.5 0-3-.4-4.3-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.4-3c-.3-.4 0-.5.2-.7l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5v-.5c0-.1-.5-1.3-.7-1.8-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.3.3-.9.9-.9 2.2s.9 2.5 1 2.7c.1.2 1.8 2.8 4.4 3.9.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3z"/></svg>
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=11600852925967987399&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="quienes-somos">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">El oro se gana <span class="gold">entrenando</span></h2>
        <div class="about reveal">
          <p>Somos <strong>GOLDEN FITNESS GYM</strong>, un gimnasio en El Cerrito, Kanasín, pensado para quien quiere resultados de verdad sin pagar de más. Aquí no vendemos humo: hay equipo suficiente, gente que sabe guiarte y un ambiente donde se viene a entrenar, no a perder el tiempo.</p>
          <p>Nuestros clientes lo resumen mejor que cualquier anuncio: «un gran sitio para ejercitarte, buenos entrenadores». El área de pesas y las máquinas se mantienen listas para que tu rutina no se detenga, y los coaches están para corregir tu técnica, no solo para cobrarte la mensualidad.</p>
          <p>Las instalaciones son muy buenas y los precios son buenos — así nos describen quienes ya entrenan aquí todos los días. Si buscas un gimnasio de barrio con nivel de verdad, este es tu lugar.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ QUÉ OFRECEMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="ofrecemos">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Qué ofrecemos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Todo lo que necesitas para <span class="gold">entrenar en serio</span></h2>
        <ul class="servicios reveal">
          <li>
            <span class="medal-num" aria-hidden="true">I</span>
            <div><h3>Área de pesas y máquinas</h3><p>Equipo variado para fuerza, tonificación y cardio, listo para tu rutina.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="medal-num" aria-hidden="true">II</span>
            <div><h3>Entrenadores que corrigen tu técnica</h3><p>«Buenos entrenadores» es lo primero que la gente destaca de nosotros.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="medal-num" aria-hidden="true">III</span>
            <div><h3>Ambiente para entrenar en serio</h3><p>Piso amplio y gente enfocada en su propia rutina, día tras día.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="medal-num" aria-hidden="true">IV</span>
            <div><h3>Precios buenos</h3><p>Así los describen quienes ya entrenan aquí a diario.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ GALERÍA ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Instalaciones</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Así se ve <span class="gold">por dentro</span></h2>
        <div class="galeria reveal">
          <img src="/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen/img/foto_2.jpg" alt="Área de máquinas de pesas en GOLDEN FITNESS GYM Mulchechén" loading="lazy" width="825" height="1100" />
          <img src="/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen/img/foto_4.jpg" alt="Piso de entrenamiento con equipo de cardio y pesas en GOLDEN FITNESS GYM" loading="lazy" width="618" height="1100" />
          <img src="/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen/img/foto_5.jpg" alt="Máquina de pesas en el área de entrenamiento de GOLDEN FITNESS GYM" loading="lazy" width="825" height="1100" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ PRUEBA SOCIAL ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Prueba social</p>
        <div class="rating-hero reveal">
          <span class="sprig sprig--lg" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
          <div class="rating-num"><span class="gold">4.5</span><span class="of5">/5</span></div>
          <span class="sprig sprig--lg sprig--r" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
        </div>
        <p class="rating-sub reveal">84 reseñas en Google</p>

        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Un gran sitio para ejercitarte, buenos entrenadores»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Aroldo Jesús Rojas Pérez</strong><span>Hace un año · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="4 estrellas">★★★★☆</p>
            <blockquote>«Buenos precios, las instalaciones son muy buenas…»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Jaffet Molina</strong><span>Hace 7 años · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=11600852925967987399&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal">Dónde estamos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">El Cerrito, <span class="gold">Kanasín</span></h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">C. 75 620, El Cerrito<br />97370 Kanasín, Yuc., México</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=11600852925967987399&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>6:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>6:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>6:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>6:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>6:00–23:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>10:00–17:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=GOLDEN%20FITNESS%20GYM%20MULCHECHEN%2C%20C.%2075%20620%2C%20El%20Cerrito%2C%2097370%20Kanas%C3%ADn%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: GOLDEN FITNESS GYM Mulchechén en Kanasín, Yucatán"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Listo para entrenar donde se nota el esfuerzo?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Escríbenos y arrancamos hoy mismo.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/529994412918" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529994412918">Llamar · 999 441 2918</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo"><span class="gold">GOLDEN</span> FITNESS GYM</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Gimnasio · C. 75 620, El Cerrito, 97370 Kanasín, Yuc., México</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529994412918">999 441 2918</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/529994412918" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a> · <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Golden.Fitness.Gym.Mulchechen" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 6:00–23:00 · Sábado 10:00–17:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "GOLDEN FITNESS GYM MULCHECHEN",
    "telephone": "+529994412918",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "C. 75 620, El Cerrito",
      "addressLocality": "Kanasín",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97370",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.5",
      "reviewCount": "84"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 06:00-23:00", "Sa 10:00-17:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --bg: #0d0d0d;
      --panel: #1c1a14;
      --gold: #d4af37;
      --gold-dim: #a4842a;
      --cream: #f3ead2;
      --muted: #b8ab8c;
      --line: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.22);
      --display: "Cinzel", "Times New Roman", serif;
      --body: "Mulish", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--cream);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .gf ::selection { background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg); }
    .gf a:focus-visible,
    .gf .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--gold);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .gold { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---------- LAUREL SPRIG (elemento firma) ---------- */
    .sprig { position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 46px; height: 60px; flex: none; }
    .sprig i {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 9px;
      margin-left: -4.5px;
      background: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 3px;
      transform-origin: bottom center;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }
    .sprig i:nth-child(1) { height: 24px; transform: rotate(-40deg) translateY(-1px); }
    .sprig i:nth-child(2) { height: 32px; transform: rotate(-20deg) translateY(-3px); }
    .sprig i:nth-child(3) { height: 38px; transform: rotate(0deg)   translateY(-3px); }
    .sprig i:nth-child(4) { height: 32px; transform: rotate(20deg)  translateY(-3px); }
    .sprig i:nth-child(5) { height: 24px; transform: rotate(40deg)  translateY(-1px); }
    .sprig--r { transform: scaleX(-1); }
    .sprig--sm { width: 30px; height: 40px; }
    .sprig--sm i { width: 6px; margin-left: -3px; }
    .sprig--sm i:nth-child(1) { height: 16px; }
    .sprig--sm i:nth-child(2) { height: 22px; }
    .sprig--sm i:nth-child(3) { height: 26px; }
    .sprig--sm i:nth-child(4) { height: 22px; }
    .sprig--sm i:nth-child(5) { height: 16px; }
    .sprig--lg { width: 58px; height: 78px; }
    .sprig--lg i { width: 11px; margin-left: -5.5px; }
    .sprig--lg i:nth-child(1) { height: 30px; }
    .sprig--lg i:nth-child(2) { height: 42px; }
    .sprig--lg i:nth-child(3) { height: 50px; }
    .sprig--lg i:nth-child(4) { height: 42px; }
    .sprig--lg i:nth-child(5) { height: 30px; }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 38px);
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      background-image: url("/golden-fitness-gym-mulchechen/img/foto_1.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center 35%;
    }
    .hero-scrim {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.55) 0%, rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.72) 55%, var(--bg) 100%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 85% 0%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.16), transparent 60%);
    }
    .hero-in { position: relative; padding: 56px 0 44px; }
    .kicker {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .word {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      line-height: 0.98;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .word-gold {
      font-size: clamp(58px, 17vw, 132px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-shadow: 0 0 42px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.35);
    }
    .word-cream {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 5.6vw, 38px);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--cream);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(17px, 4.2vw, 21px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
      max-width: 36ch;
      margin: 22px 0 0;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 22px 0 0;
    }
    .badge-txt {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 9px 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--cream);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
      margin: 22px 0 0;
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--gold); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin: 26px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 26px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--gold); color: #1a1608; }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: #e4c157; }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--line); color: var(--cream); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 15px; padding: 12px 20px; }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 72px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--panel); }
    .sec-kicker {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 12.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: #d9cfb4; }
    .about strong { color: var(--cream); }

    /* ---------- SERVICIOS ---------- */
    .servicios {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .servicios li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 22px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .servicios li:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .medal-num {
      position: relative;
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      flex: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid var(--gold);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .medal-num::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 4px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.45);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .servicios h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin: 4px 0 6px;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .servicios p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15.5px; }

    /* ---------- GALERÍA ---------- */
    .galeria {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .galeria img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .rating-hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }
    .rating-num {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 12vw, 76px);
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .rating-num .of5 { font-size: 0.4em; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; }
    .rating-sub {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 0 0 36px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 22px 22px 20px;
    }
    .rev-stars {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .rev figcaption {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--muted); }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .dir { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--cream); }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 19px;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15.5px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--cream); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: #1a1608; background: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: #1a1608;
      color: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
      filter: grayscale(0.4) invert(0.92) contrast(0.9);
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: #1a1608;
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 7vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 600; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: #1a1608; color: var(--gold); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: #2a230f; }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(26, 22, 8, 0.55); color: #1a1608; }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: #1a1608; }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--cream);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--cream); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: #7a7057; font-size: 12.5px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .sec { padding: 104px 0; }
      .servicios { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; column-gap: 48px; }
      .servicios li:nth-child(2) { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .servicios li:nth-last-child(2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .galeria { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); max-width: 720px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 420px; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
